            "description": [
                "Samsung's ENERGY STAR Certified Front Load washer has 4.5 cu. ft. capacity to fit more in every load and cut down on laundry time. It is equipped with Vibration Reduction Technology+ to reduce noise for quiet washing and features Self Clean+ to eliminate 99% of bacteria that can form in the drum.    Large 4.5 cu ft. Capacity for fewer loads, less time in the laundry room and more time doing the things you love    Do your laundry without disturbing anyone at any time and in any place. Innovative Vibration Reduction Technology+ reduces noise and vibration for quiet washing    Keep your washer fresh and clean with Self Clean+ technology, which eliminates 99% of bacteria that can form in any washer drum, Self Clean+ will notify you every 40 wash cycles when it is time for a cleaning    ENERGY STAR certified, so you can save money by using less energy without sacrificing performance or functionality    Easy troubleshooting from the convenience of your smartphone. Smart Care interacts with your washer and dryer to perform an immediate diagnosis and offer quick solutions    Swirl+ Drum Interior for improved drum pattern that extracts more water more quickly during the rinsing cycle and prevents fabrics from snagging during washing    Closet-Depth Fit gives your home a sleek, modern look with a seamless design. This washer has a shallow depth, so it fits within your existing laundry space without sacrificing any capacity, thanks to our new, wider drum. Also, a new control panel design provides better visibility, so it is easy to use when stacked    With a Samsung Riser, your washer or dryer is compliant with the Americans with Disabilities Act (ADA), making loading and unloading easier. Also aiding the visually and hearing impaired, audio assistance plays a different sound for each option and braille is next to key control panel buttons    UL Certified    10 Preset Washing Cycles    6 Additional Washing Options - Provide optimal care for all fabric types    5 Temperature Levels    Matching Dryers: DVE45T6000W (Electric) and DVG45T6000W (Gas)    Matching Pedestal: WE402NW    Matching Riser: WE272NW     Click here for more information on Electronic Recycling Programs       California residents"
            ],
